data.description: Do not miss this special offering to own this welcoming and amazing 2 bedroom, 1 bath cottage with detached 1 car garage that is ideally located for exploring the Hudson Valley's many attractions. Spend your days hiking scenic trails, touring local wineries, spending the day at the beautiful gardens of Innisfree, or browsing charming restaurants and boutiques in Millbrook's village center. Come take a look at this adorable home that is only 90 minutes from NYC and close to Taconic State Parkway for easy commute.
